txt.en:
'Nar, we can't go on like this!

'We haven't sent Shelob anything since Lugbúrz fell, and I think Her Ladyship's gotten a bit spoiled. Either that, or She's in a foul mood from whatever the Elf-warrior did to her....

'When Her Ladyship is hungry, there's only one thing for it. The garrison's going to have to get by with a few less Orcs, or we'll all be for the pot!

'Gather up eight Orcs, and make it quick! We'd best get this over with!'
Captain Róglarg enlists your aid in gathering new sacrifices to be made to Shelob.
Report to Captain Róglarg in Cirith Ungol
Gathered Orcs to sacrifice to Shelob ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
'Well, that lot there ought to do it! A sorry business, this, but it has to be done!'
Captain Róglarg can be found in the courtyard of Cirith Ungol.\n\nYou have gathered the sacrifices and should now report back to Captain Róglarg.
Orcs can be found throughout Cirith Ungol.\n\nCaptain Róglarg has commanded you to gather eight Orcs to be sacrificed to Shelob.
